#

Classic New York Style Cheeseburger

$15.99
800 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinComfort Food

Tags:

BurgerAmericanComfort FoodBeef

Description

A juicy cheeseburger topped with aged cheddar and house-made pickles, served with crispy garlic herb fries.

Ingredients

  • Ground Beef: 1 lb
  • Aged Cheddar Cheese: 4 slices
  • Brioche Buns: 4
  • Lettuce: 4 leaves
  • Tomato: 1 large, sliced
  • Pickles: 1 cup, diced
  • Garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • Fresh Herbs (Rosemary, Thyme): 2 tbsp each, chopped
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
  • Ketchup: 1 cup
  • Hot Sauce: 2 tbsp
